main event: On June 30, 1966, an observer reported seeing a bright, green light that pulsated and was visible for about 5 seconds from the ground.
interesting points: The sighting lasted about 5 seconds,The object was described as a bright green light,Pulsating light was the primary characteristic reported,No photographs or physical evidence were collected,This incident has been recorded in Project Blue Book documents.
witness description: The observer was a civilian reporting the sighting.
